{
  "_doc": [
    "Tests the effect of strong per-class data skew. Each user has a data_percent plus a per-label",
    "retention factor: 1.0 keeps the full fair share for that participant's assigned label,",
    "while 0.2 keeps 20% of the fair share for all other labels.",
    "Each participant focuses on one distinct label: H1 -> label 0, H2 -> label 1, ..., H10 -> label 9.",
    "Expectation: users with complete coverage of their assigned label perform better on that label and",
    "earn higher reputation when their specialization is useful."
